Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Gary Greene -

data.description: Beautiful large remodeled ranch style home in the heart of Waller and close to Field Store and its not in a flood zone! 3.325 unrestricted acres with added bonus property surrounded by  ranches which makes a wonderful extended view. 12x20 storage shed, 3 carports attached to two 1-car garages used for parking cars or a workshop, plus a greenhouse. Front porch with a view of a sprawling red oak that covers the front yard and a side deck. Newer Aerobic system, HVAC with solar panel to help reduce that light bill and all new ducts installed within last 6 years.  If you're trying to move to Waller this is a must see, it doesn't get any better than this. Perfect location with quick access to Brenham, Cypress, Magnolia and Tomball.
